@{
    ViewBag.Title = "Home Page";
}

<div class="jumbotron">
    
    @if (!this.User.Identity.IsAuthenticated)
    {   <h1>Favor service</h1>
        <p class="lead"><strong>Favor</strong> is an online platform which provides the most amazing offer-trading experience in the world built through an awesome community</p>
        <p class="text-center">100% satisfaction guarantee <i class="material-icons">done_all</i></p>
        <hr />
        <div class="text-center"><p><a href="/Account/Login" class="btn btn-primary btn-lg">Continue &raquo;</a></p></div>
    }
    else
    {<h1 class="text-center">Welcome to <b>Favor</b></h1>
    <p class="lead text-center">We hope you will enjoy your stay here and find what you are looking for!</p>
    }
</div>

<div class="row">
    
    
    <div class="col-md-4">
        <h2>Concept</h2>
        <p>
           <b>Favor</b> provides the fastest trade-offering service in the world surrounded by amazing people...
        </p>
        <p><a class="btn btn-default" href="https://go.microsoft.com/fwlink/?LinkId=301865">Learn more &raquo;</a></p>
    </div>
    
    
    <div class="col-md-4">
        <h2>Staff</h2>
        <p>Learn more about the founders of this idea.</p>
        <p><button class="btn btn-default" data-toggle="modal" data-target="#myModal">The Crew &raquo;</button></p>
        
        <div class="modal fade" id="myModal" tabindex="-1" role="dialog" aria-labelledby="myModalLabel" aria-hidden="true">
            <div class="modal-dialog" 
                    style="
                    padding-top: 20px;
                    padding-left: 20px;
                    padding-right: 30px;
                    border-right-width: 30px;
                    margin-right: 900px;">

                <div class="modal-content col-md-pull-12">
                    <div class="modal-header">
                        <button type="button" class="close" data-dismiss="modal" aria-hidden="true">&times;</button>
                        <h4 class="modal-title" id="myModalLabel">Modal title</h4>
                    </div>
                    <div class="modal-body "><img href="~/Content/img/favor.jpg" />
                        Far far away, behind the word mountains, far from the countries Vokalia and Consonantia, there live the blind texts. Separated they live in Bookmarksgrove right at the coast of the Semantics, a large language ocean. A small river named Duden flows by their place and supplies it with the necessary regelialia. It is a paradisematic country, in which roasted parts of sentences fly into your mouth. Even the all-powerful Pointing has no control about the blind texts it is an almost unorthographic life One day however a small line of blind text by the name of Lorem Ipsum decided to leave for the far World of Grammar.
                    </div>
                    <div class="modal-footer">
                        <button type="button" class="btn btn-default btn-simple" data-dismiss="modal">Close</button>
                        <button type="button" class="btn btn-info btn-simple">Save</button>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    
    </div>
    
    
    <div class="col-md-4">
        <h2>Help</h2>
        <p>Have any troubles or complains?</p>
        <button type="button" class="btn btn-default" data-toggle="popover" data-placement="top" title="FavorService@gmail.com">Email us</button>
    </div>
</div>